Subject:Re: [child_lit] Blind protagonists
One of the viewpoint characters in my THE STORYTELLER'S BEADS showed herself to be blind :> after I read a fascinating sentence in a nonfiction book about the exodus of the Ethiopian Jews about a blind girl who walked all the way to the Sudan with her hand on her brother's shoulder.  JaneK 

